{"tid":2370814,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【直擊單位】二手反彈 沙田第一城2房又重上600萬","createTime":"2021-01-18T09:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T07:46:08.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"71d3f9c09d53f5a742355ffd401988ade6839134","tid":2370814,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:50:14.000Z","msg":"疫情雖反覆，惟剛性需求大，帶動二手交投，沙田第一城本月暫錄逾25宗成交，2房重上600萬元。美聯物業聯席區域經理翁凱傑指出，沙田第一城9座高層D室，實用面積327平方呎，以600萬元易手，實用呎價18,349元。據悉，同座同室高3層單位曾於2020年以600萬元轉售，相同價錢就要買低幾層。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2016年以360萬元購入，持貨5年帳面獲利240萬元，單位升值67%。"},{"pid":"07b717fe47be4b8c0c018fcc1a6a84373590bca7","tid":2370814,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e8278fe26a129911c130978eb5d5ffcc374af6","tid":2370814,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"上車盤永遠大把人接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6636fc9e995e99defc5683a22315731538ff5381","tid":2370814,"uid":14965,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:52:02.000Z","msg":"仆街 咩世界<br />\n<br />\n全世界都大亂都升 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"56a2ab3b11328d40e8bd782dd5b4608f1e02eb6c","tid":2370814,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"有幾多人追蹤樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2d971a8d9c71f75497b85f39459343a5adc866","tid":2370814,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"蓋清又賺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682889c1a878a987f05b1aab7ffcf2abd6f2dda9","tid":2370814,"uid":73269